            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1627376633929-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>plant-based creamy veg gnocchi </strong>topped with the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>salad</strong> with your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 5,
